## Why It Matters
Tools like KQL, Defender and Sentinel are the what analyst actually use to find, verify and discover the scope of suspcicious activity.  These tools answer whether the alert is real, how many devices are affected, when and where it started, the context of the incident and recommended mitigation and remediation steps. 


## Practical Security Relevance
Microsoft Defender helps analysts see the full attack chain, increase the speed of investigation and containment.
